            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 48,
              "body": "also why go against the spec in this way? we could also say that such records are ignored and then we don't conflict with the spec.",
              "createdAt": "2023-12-20T11:18:15Z",
              "updatedAt": "2023-12-20T11:20:11Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 93,
              "body": "maybe clarify? the idea is that the party running that server now knows your key material and could abuse that if they also controlled some other server?",
